OL,3,CPetrol theft rises nearly 25% since
OL,4,Cstart of year, new data shows
OL,6,FNew data given to ITV News shows theft
OL,7,Fof petrol and diesel is up by almost a
OL,8,Fquarter over the last couple of months.
OL,10,FSome criminals are filling up more
OL,11,Fthan one tank at a time.
OL,13,FNow industry insiders are warning that
OL,14,Fit's creating an increasing public
OL,15,Fdanger.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
