OL,3,CPetrol theft rises nearly 25% since
OL,4,Cstart of year, new data shows
OL,6,FSecurity expert Michelle Henchoz of
OL,7,FForecourt Eye said: "I think driving
OL,8,Finto a forecourt, headlights on,
OL,9,Ffilling up the car, leaving the engine
OL,10,Frunning, leaving the door open,
OL,11,Fwearing certain face coverings, you
OL,12,Fknow, baseball caps.
OL,14,F"And then when someone is filling up a
OL,15,Fvehicle, or actually filling up cans
OL,16,Fin the backseat and then when they're
OL,17,Fleaving the forecourt, you've
OL,18,Fbasically got a travelling petrol
OL,19,Fstation which can be a really
OL,20,Fdangerous thing for other people on
OL,21,Fthe road."
