OL,3,CPetrol theft rises nearly 25% since
OL,4,Cstart of year, new data shows
OL,6,FRising petrol prices don't matter much
OL,7,Fto an increasing number of drivers -
OL,8,Fthey're not paying.
OL,10,FAs fuel prices surge amid disruption
OL,11,Fcaused by the war in Iran, the petrol
OL,12,Findustry fears that many motorists see
OL,13,Fthis as a victimless crime affecting
OL,14,Fonly hyper-wealthy fuel conglomerates.
OL,16,FRachael King is a forecourt manager in
OL,17,FGloucestershire running three
OL,18,Fforecourts for a small family business.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
