OL,3,CPetrol theft rises nearly 25% since
OL,4,Cstart of year, new data shows
OL,6,FShe told us: "The other thing you'll
OL,7,Fsee is the passenger filling up rather
OL,8,Fthan the driver, therefore the driver
OL,9,Fcan stay in their seat.
OL,11,F"And as soon as they finish, they can
OL,12,Fdrive off.
OL,14,F"Maybe trying to use a pump that's the
OL,15,Ffurthest away on a forecourt, or the
OL,16,Fother option is a pump nearest to the
OL,17,Froad cause it's easiest to get away."
