OL,3,CPetrol theft rises nearly 25% since
OL,4,Cstart of year, new data shows
OL,6,FFigures given to ITV News exclusively
OL,7,Fby the security firm Forecourt Eye
OL,8,Fshow a 23% rise in forecourt fuel
OL,9,Fthefts, from 9,089 incidents in
OL,10,FJanuary and February, to 11,170 in
OL,11,FMarch and April, with 432,409 litres
OL,12,Fstolen in that period.
OL,14,FWith an increasing number of automatic
OL,15,Fnumber plate recognition cameras,
OL,16,Fforecourts are doing more to stop fuel
OL,17,Ftheft.
OL,19,FBut they say there's little they can
OL,20,Fdo to stop the relentless price rises
OL,21,Fthat are making this problem worse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
